Well he might. But I can't mind much about it. Oh well my mother had aye plenty to do, mending and whatnot you know. Just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3749059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3502717\charrsid14223522 Did they ever get away out in the evening by themselves?
