Oh well, they might - visit their - visit - their friends or the likes of that but - aye, they never - aye, they never - they were never much out the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3749059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3502717\charrsid14223522 What about your father belonging to any other kind of club?
