{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Stow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. And they - then - aye, and the - the coals came to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Stow{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} to you see, and it was carted over the hill.
