 there was young - driver, his nickname I can - his name I had to think to - but I canna mind his nickname but his - his right name, but his name was Pause, because he always said, if - you know, what time will you - you get up? Oh, he says, just pause a 
little. Just pause a little. Then of course the folk had to get out the break sometime and walk up the hill you know. Up the steep bit. Oh it was a great affair.
